Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先遣队在后续部队到达前消灭接近谷风机和紬的奇居子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让奇居子靠近谷风机和紬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这么多 没完没了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别叫苦了 一定要保护好他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们被发现了 它们朝这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管它们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的任务是保护谷风和䌷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐木主任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在有多少架隼风可以投入战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投入隼风？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个发射口还只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组成大编队可是要花些时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 从已经就绪的机体开始依次发射出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长 我要申报由隼风执行的奇居子扫荡作战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将谷风机他们作为诱饵 让大群奇居子集中到地表一处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不失去一架机体地拿下行星九号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把谷风他们当作诱饵？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了将潜伏在行星九号的奇居子聚集到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要全歼它们非这样不可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是出于战术需要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不失去一架机体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 你试试
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诱饵被干掉就前功尽弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要保护好他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会让他们平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇居子！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弦打
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别大意哦 弦打
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,势威 你啊 又抢风头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二批后续部队已到达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三批 第四批也将很快会合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到达的机体迅速展开攻击队形
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动用全部火力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼风组成的奇居子讨伐队 全部到达轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发动总攻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扫荡牠们 一只也别放过！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.07,0:11:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.27,0:12:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各机确认自己负责的区域 别重迭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人本体剩余100只
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,焰 往你那里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…窜来窜去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩余90只
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩余80只
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩余70只
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩余60只
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩余50只
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩余40只
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩余30只
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩余20只
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差一口气了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认最后一只奇居子已泡状分解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌奇居子剩余本体0只
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经全部歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了啊…面对那么多的奇居子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:12:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是换成以前 简直是不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.02,0:13:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经控制住行星九号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场扫荡战打得非常漂亮 绿川司令助理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了 紬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊 伊札那呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这呢 紬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.97,0:13:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 都是多亏了紬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你来救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能以那种状态回希德尼娅来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头盔和操纵服都连备用的一起报销了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法在保障驾驶员安全的同时排出那东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去从未有过被切离本体的胞衣自行攻击人类的事例
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个胞衣看上去也不太危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风 你能抱着紬飞上来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这什么姿势…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我会不会很重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 紬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒担心谷风会忍不住非礼胞衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.73,0:15:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么想 莎玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全机 准备归航
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星白…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:01.94,eyecatch,NTP,994,0,0,,希德尼娅百景　隼风起降船坞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:05.01,eyecatch,NTP,923,0,0,,希德尼娅百景　落合旧地下研究设施内温室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功进入行星九号的卫星轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大众合船的情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无变化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下算是告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过既然来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.43,0:16:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}本日 希德尼娅成功进入了行星九号的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}行星九号拥有丰富的资源
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}外围星环是易守难攻的天然要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}司令部表示
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我们就此获得了在必将到来的与大众合船的战斗中极其重要的阵地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不能回头了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再过不久 一百年前没能实现的梦想就要成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:17:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的 转生为究极生物的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风长道 因你在占领行星九号的战役中功勋卓著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现授予你八机掌位勋章
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你成为骑士了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 不胜感激
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多 多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说谷风 把勋章给我看看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.22,0:17:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 炼 你也太不拿自己当外人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,焰你别管我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你 谷风长道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岐神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待你今后的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要向你道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你救了紬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岐神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星白…啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个胞衣怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前作为贵重的标本保存起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为重要的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…需要有冗余
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,授勋是早已被遗忘的制度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.97,0:18:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过用来激励士气倒似乎是上上之策啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小林！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再利用那孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类的心是脆弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有英雄的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要撑过漫长的战争是多么艰难
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你 应该都十分清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小林…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 都还没回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.37,0:20:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好烫 好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不许这样了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我陪你一起去道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的 长道是不会讨厌䌷的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.26,0:21:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我擅自把你的制服拿来穿了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 不要再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.37,0:21:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来䌷还有这样的能力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过为什么要变成星白的样子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:22:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为 谷风先生因为没能阻止星白战死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直对此感到后悔而痛苦着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我变成星白的样子对他说 不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.90,0:22:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样他就能打起精神来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.32,0:22:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风和红天蛾战斗时一定很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.55,0:22:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.20,0:22:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.17,0:22:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和红天蛾战斗对䌷来说也一样痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长道？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.90,0:22:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你们都在这里啊 哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.65,0:23:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风先生 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.26,0:23:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才大声嚷嚷 对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来 我在这附近䌷能到达的地方发现了一家无人货摊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.62,0:23:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.65,0:23:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.55,0:23:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 我这周也还什么都没吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.00,0:23:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.27,0:23:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.65,0:23:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.22,0:23:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是 谷风长道操纵士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.65,0:23:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候承蒙照顾 多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.77,0:23:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里 我才是冒犯失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.67,0:24:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请自便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.77,0:24:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来泡茶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.65,0:24:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不必了 我还有地方要去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.05,0:24:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.92,0:24:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎随时再来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.85,0:24:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我会准备饭团的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.72,0:24:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多…多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.92,0:24:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.35,0:24:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一开始住院时的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.25,0:24:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候的偷米贼原来就是谷风操纵士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.42,0:24:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉 说些多余的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.92,0:25:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时给你们添了麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.20,0:25:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.47,0:25:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.10,0:25:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？喂 你在那干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.75,0:25:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你是…谷风操纵士
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.84,0:25:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.53,0:25:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.62,0:25:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通行许可证
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.27,0:25:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 是要回老家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.47,0:25:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.20,0:25:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 这袋米
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.80,0:25:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请带上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.27,0:26:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢 谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.29,0:26:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}长道看好 不要上去 by 广树
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.17,0:26:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.15,0:26:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 没听您的话
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.10,0:26:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我很庆幸自己离开了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.77,0:26:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经历了许多事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.02,0:26:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.82,0:27:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得越来越喜欢希德尼娅了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.72,0:27:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了 长道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.15,0:27:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.47,0:27:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 大米
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.75,0:27:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 好好吃一顿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.10,0:27:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饿着肚子可没法战斗 嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.08,0:27:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.12,0:28:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还得到了这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.15,0:28:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是虚拟训练装置
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.95,0:28:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了打败奇居子进行特训的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.70,0:28:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要试试看吗 长道
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.45,0:28:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.95,0:28:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长道
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.95,0:28:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是要成为保护希德尼娅的操纵士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.15,0:28:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就要有再难过也要有继续战斗的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.60,0:28:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇居子可不会等你哭干眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.35,0:28:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看着
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.40,0:28:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我教你怎么和奇居子战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.50,0:29:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.20,0:29:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.17,0:29:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去驾驶继卫
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.67,0:29:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇604 已通过第一警戒线
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.95,0:29:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离18万千单位
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.92,0:29:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西队12部执勤机 抓紧准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.10,0:29:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来将开始讨伐奇604
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.35,0:29:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫人队各机 依次出击
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.00,0:32:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风班 四机掌位
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.25,0:32:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.85,0:32:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.72,0:32:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望您能暂时替我保管一下 爷爷
